title: #92Noon Twins Talker Tuesday
description: Twins president Dave St Peter and GM Thad Levine both join, Gleeman and John Bonnes in studio as well, pumping up the Twins/Astros Wildcard playoff series! Final hour, more baseball, plus news of Titans/Vikings being impacted by the virus.
